      "confidence": 0.82051307
    },
    {
      "sentiment": "NEUTRAL",
      "speaker": "A",
      "text": "It's not 100% certain, but if you see these things on the product listing, they definitely have a brand registry.",
      "start": 9680,
      "end": 18000,
      "confidence": 0.82883334
    },
    {
      "sentiment": "NEUTRAL",
      "speaker": "A",
      "text": "So the first thing is, if you go to the product page and click on these, if it leads to a storefront like this, then they definitely have a brand registry.",
