      "end": 31130,
      "confidence": 0.69411707
    },
    {
      "sentiment": "NEUTRAL",
      "speaker": "A",
      "text": "Or if you scroll down and see pictures, some pictures, some text, but at least pictures in the product description section, then that's also a sign they have a brand registry.",
